<br /><b>BULUTLI HISOBLASH TIZIMLARIDA XAVFSIZLIK MEXANIZMLARI</b>
<br />
<br />
<br /><i>Xudoykulov Z.T. (TATU, dotsent)</i>
<br /><i>Karimov A.A. (TATU, assistent)</i>
